<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 04:09:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙以色列人质的绝望困境正在削弱公众对战争的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/the-desperate-plight-of-israeli-hostages-is-eating-away-at-public-support-for-the-war/0000018d-3820-d523-adfd-3d7e36ba0000</link><description>加沙的血腥行动持续的时间越长，以色列右翼声称以色列国防军正在“为解救人质而战”的说法对公众来说就越不那么空洞。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/the-desperate-plight-of-israeli-hostages-is-eating-away-at-public-support-for-the-war/0000018d-3820-d523-adfd-3d7e36ba0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军司令表示，以色列军队将从汗尤尼斯致命事件中吸取教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-live/israeli-army-will-learn-lessons-from-deadly-khan-yunis-incident-idf-chief-says/0000018d-3976-d523-adfd-3d7e56fd0000</link><description>以色列军队在加沙边境附近拆除建筑物，导致 21 名士兵在加沙丧生；哈马斯枪手向附近的一辆坦克发射火箭弹，同时发生爆炸，导致建筑物倒塌，里面有士兵。 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：过去 24 小时内有 195 人因以色列袭击而死亡 ■ 报告：卡车叙利亚和伊拉克边境附近发生袭击和爆炸 ■ 埃及高级官员表示，哈马斯拒绝了以色列的提议，此前 Axios 报道称，以色列通过调解人向哈马斯提供了一项协议，其中包括长达两个月的停战协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-live/israeli-army-will-learn-lessons-from-deadly-khan-yunis-incident-idf-chief-says/0000018d-3976-d523-adfd-3d7e56fd0000</guid></item><item><title>经过十年的拖延，以色列最高法院裁定苏丹寻求庇护者必须获得临时居民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-supreme-court-rules-sudanese-asylum-seekers-be-granted-temporary-resident-status/0000018d-3733-d32b-adcf-f773bdcf0000</link><description>犹太援助组织 HIAS 副主任表示：“我们希望这只是迈向公平和适当庇护制度的第一步……规范临时身份带来的不仅仅是健康保险和社会福利，而是一种感觉安全的</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 19:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-supreme-court-rules-sudanese-asylum-seekers-be-granted-temporary-resident-status/0000018d-3733-d32b-adcf-f773bdcf0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，哈马斯拒绝以色列为期两个月的停火提议以换取人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/hamas-reportedly-rejects-two-month-cease-fire-proposal-by-israel-in-exchange-for-hostages/0000018d-36f9-d6f3-a7af-3fffb8100000</link><description>以色列政府发言人周二发表讲话，没有证实已提出要约，但表示正在努力遣返人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 19:10:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/hamas-reportedly-rejects-two-month-cease-fire-proposal-by-israel-in-exchange-for-hostages/0000018d-36f9-d6f3-a7af-3fffb8100000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的严重伤亡引发以色列公众对停火和潜在人质协议的讨论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/heavy-casualties-in-gaza-spark-israeli-public-discourse-on-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018d-371f-d32b-adcf-f77fb7860000</link><description>加沙与哈马斯的战斗开始类似于第二次黎巴嫩战争和第一次黎巴嫩战争期间的安全区 ■ 在没有取得明确和决定性胜利的情况下，以色列选择将重点放在敌人的伤亡人数上</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:59:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/heavy-casualties-in-gaza-spark-israeli-public-discourse-on-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018d-371f-d32b-adcf-f77fb7860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 2023 年度鸟类比赛获胜者：迷失的花斑丛林聊天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/winner-of-israels-bird-of-the-year-2023-contest-a-lost-pied-bush-chat/0000018d-3725-d32b-adcf-f7671da60000</link><description>这只聊天鸟是知更鸟的近亲，它可能来自伊朗，它勇敢地在观鸟者面前炫耀了几个月，而不是躲在同名的灌木丛中</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/winner-of-israels-bird-of-the-year-2023-contest-a-lost-pied-bush-chat/0000018d-3725-d32b-adcf-f7671da60000</guid></item><item><title>“我们以色列人对美国的依赖比我们想象的要严重得多”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-23/ty-article-podcast/we-in-israel-are-far-more-dependent-on-the-u-s-than-we-ever-knew/0000018d-36f2-dbf8-abdf-bef6eeb50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-23/ty-article-podcast/we-in-israel-are-far-more-dependent-on-the-u-s-than-we-ever-knew/0000018d-36f2-dbf8-abdf-bef6eeb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙最血腥的一天引发了人们对接下来会发生什么的疑问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-bloodiest-day-in-gaza-raises-questions-over-what-comes-next/0000018d-36ad-d6f3-a7af-3fefd1e90000</link><description>一次事件中 21 名以色列国防军士兵丧生，证明了涉及大量爆炸物的地面行动的危险性。它还对在边境建立缓冲区的优点提出质疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 15:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-bloodiest-day-in-gaza-raises-questions-over-what-comes-next/0000018d-36ad-d6f3-a7af-3fefd1e90000</guid></item><item><title>真主党两周内第二次袭击以色列北部的以色列国防军空军基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-idf-airbase-in-northern-israel-for-second-time-in-two-weeks/0000018d-368a-dbf8-abdf-bede69f70000</link><description>真主党表示，它发射这些导弹是为了回应以色列暗杀真主党和圣城旅指挥官的事件，并在检测到以色列空军基地存在“漏洞”后；以色列国防军报告“轻微损坏”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 14:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-idf-airbase-in-northern-israel-for-second-time-in-two-weeks/0000018d-368a-dbf8-abdf-bede69f70000</guid></item><item><title>“总统不能否决我的投票”：拜登在首次民主党初选中面临加沙考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-president-cant-veto-my-vote-biden-faces-gaza-test-in-first-democratic-primary/0000018d-35c2-d6df-adcf-35d3f6580000</link><description>一些活动人士发誓要在周二的新罕布什尔州初选中写下“停火”，以抗议总统乔·拜登对以色列与哈马斯战争的态度。由于党内不和，拜登的名字根本没有出现在选票上</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-president-cant-veto-my-vote-biden-faces-gaza-test-in-first-democratic-primary/0000018d-35c2-d6df-adcf-35d3f6580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列清空了北部地区。现在官员们担心撤离人员在战后不会返回家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-emptied-its-north-now-officials-fear-evacuees-wont-return-home-after-the-war/0000018d-35df-d6df-adcf-35df4bb70000</link><description>加沙战争期间，居住在黎巴嫩边境附近的近8万人被疏散或逃离；一项调查显示，只有 60% 的人确定自己想回国</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-emptied-its-north-now-officials-fear-evacuees-wont-return-home-after-the-war/0000018d-35df-d6df-adcf-35df4bb70000</guid></item><item><title>与 10 月 7 日受害者一起工作的高级精神科医生：以色列需要希望的处方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/senior-psychiatrist-working-with-october-7-victims-israel-needs-a-prescription-of-hope/0000018d-35d3-db8f-a7df-37f3de210000</link><description>什洛莫·门德洛维奇教授表示，仍然很难估计有多少以色列人会患上创伤后应激障碍（“估计有 60,000 到 600,000 个新病例”）。他解释了为什么团体治疗可能是一场灾难，并建议以色列必须采取哪些措施才能康复</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:45:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/senior-psychiatrist-working-with-october-7-victims-israel-needs-a-prescription-of-hope/0000018d-35d3-db8f-a7df-37f3de210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队围攻汗尤尼斯，数千名流离失所的加沙人逃往南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-besieges-khan-yunis-as-thousands-of-displaced-gazans-flee-further-south/0000018d-363b-d81e-abdf-3e3f65480000</link><description>以色列军队表示，他们正在深入城市，打击哈马斯的关键地点，居民报告称，士兵包围了两家医院，并阻止医疗队到达医院</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-besieges-khan-yunis-as-thousands-of-displaced-gazans-flee-further-south/0000018d-363b-d81e-abdf-3e3f65480000</guid></item><item><title>加沙获释人质称哈马斯对待女性人质“像玩偶一样”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-released-from-gaza-says-hamas-treated-female-hostages-like-dolls/0000018d-35d9-db8f-a7df-37fb5cf70000</link><description>“首相和内阁不会因为她们怀孕而归来感到不安吗？” ■ 在以色列议会性暴力和性别暴力受害者会议上，被扣押在加沙的女性人质的家人恳求释放她们</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-released-from-gaza-says-hamas-treated-female-hostages-like-dolls/0000018d-35d9-db8f-a7df-37fb5cf70000</guid></item><item><title>21名士兵丧生，这是以色列对加沙发动地面进攻以来最严重的事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/21-soldiers-killed-in-deadliest-incident-for-israel-since-start-of-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018d-35af-d81e-abdf-3daf470e0000</link><description>部队在距离边境 600 米的建筑物中埋设地雷，将其夷为平地。哈马斯战士向守卫士兵的坦克和建筑物发射火箭弹，导致士兵倒塌</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/21-soldiers-killed-in-deadliest-incident-for-israel-since-start-of-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018d-35af-d81e-abdf-3daf470e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争助推埃尔多安竞选，土耳其与哈马斯保持密切关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-is-giving-a-boost-to-erdogan-election-campaign/0000018d-3556-d81e-abdf-3d5e04970000</link><description>当埃尔多安利用亲巴勒斯坦情绪让他的政党在即将举行的地方选举中取得胜利时，土耳其发现自己被排除在有关加沙未来的讨论之外。尽管如此，该国仍将在哈马斯的命运中发挥关键作用</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-is-giving-a-boost-to-erdogan-election-campaign/0000018d-3556-d81e-abdf-3d5e04970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军司令表示，以色列军队将从汗尤尼斯致命事件中吸取教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-live/three-israeli-officers-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-345d-d6df-adcf-35dd49d60000</link><description>以色列军队在加沙边境附近拆除建筑物，导致 21 名士兵在加沙丧生；哈马斯枪手向附近的一辆坦克发射火箭弹，同时发生爆炸，导致建筑物倒塌，里面有士兵。 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：过去 24 小时内有 195 人因以色列袭击而死亡 ■ 报告：卡车叙利亚和伊拉克边境附近发生袭击和爆炸 ■ 埃及高级官员表示，哈马斯拒绝了以色列的提议，此前 Axios 报道称，以色列通过调解人向哈马斯提供了一项协议，其中包括长达两个月的停战协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-live/three-israeli-officers-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-345d-d6df-adcf-35dd49d60000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列官员因涉嫌向巴勒斯坦人出售数千份入境许可证而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-officers-arrested-on-suspicion-of-selling-entry-permits-to-palestinians/0000018d-333e-d6df-adcf-33bf7c6d0000</link><description>两名主要嫌疑人是一名职业军官和他的父亲，警方在他的家中发现了 74 万谢克尔现金和 121 块金锭</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-officers-arrested-on-suspicion-of-selling-entry-permits-to-palestinians/0000018d-333e-d6df-adcf-33bf7c6d0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属：以色列愿意为新协议做出让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-told-hostages-families-israel-would-make-concessions-for-new-deal/0000018d-332d-d81e-abdf-3b2dcf850000</link><description>消息人士称，总理似乎愿意在释放巴勒斯坦囚犯的数量和身份问题上做出妥协——300人在内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷的家外示威</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-told-hostages-families-israel-would-make-concessions-for-new-deal/0000018d-332d-d81e-abdf-3b2dcf850000</guid></item><item><title>周一，三名以色列国防军军官在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/three-israeli-army-officers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-monday/0000018d-328a-d81e-abdf-3a8e3dfe0000</link><description>这三人分别是大卫·纳蒂·阿尔法西少校、伊莱·利维少校和埃亚尔·梅沃拉奇·特维托上尉，均在加沙地带南部的一场战斗中阵亡。据军方称，自地面行动开始以来，已有200名以色列士兵在加沙丧生</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/three-israeli-army-officers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-monday/0000018d-328a-d81e-abdf-3a8e3dfe0000</guid></item></channel></rss>